{"tid":2158001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選完，也忍完了。告訴大家，九二共識是什麼","createTime":"2020-08-15T12:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T13:48:50.000Z","uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"891eb1844bf4089a29265ecacd6fbd0e38ad47be","tid":2158001,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T12:06:23.000Z","msg":"九二共識，就是一國兩制，貨真價實的一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n它是建立自治政體，是中國取得台灣主權的重大憲法部署，即是一國兩制，而且是一國兩制的最關鍵一步。<br />\n<br />\n這個，共產黨是心知肚明的，於是派遣嘍囉在選舉論壇抹黑泛綠，也助長那些即將滅黨的候選人圍攻民進黨。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜在電視台的論壇的結語公開講：高雄發大財、棋子還是塞子、政治放兩旁，民眾放中間。這是一國兩制的宣言。<br />\n<br />\n故此，他們發動網軍來對付民進黨，使得中共在政權崩潰之前，不給台灣獨立建國的機會。<br />\n<br />\n由中共的反應可以看到，九二共識即是一國兩制，這也是國民黨和泛藍政黨一致反對台獨的原因<br />\n<br />\n 至於那些老共資助的偽裝泛綠政黨，抗拒維持現狀，原因也是好簡單，九二共識是真一國兩制，而且是可以在中共支援之下執行的統一議程。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd7b9fb1164b4467541d5412319dec6c8de6402","tid":2158001,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"淨係睇第一句都知係陳雲"},{"pid":"49c0d8754ab32c73edee1bbf471211886d89a22c","tid":2158001,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5fd7b9fb1164b4467541d5412319dec6c8de6402","tid":2158001,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"淨係睇第一句都知係陳雲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T12:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa886fae7feba099fac30ef48158ca88d22a276b","tid":2158001,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T12:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6cf9792bcd681f6f7912d1bceed5e7cd1843fb","tid":2158001,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28073be94251ae1169d1e9a59e8071f33b517e4","tid":2158001,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知九二共識係一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf78918906097d907e583ccce6785d30eea4eff","tid":2158001,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}